@@TJvToolBar.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvToolBar object.
Description
  Use \Create to create and initialize a new TJvToolBar object.
  
  \Create calls the inherited \Create method, then sets the initial values for the toolbar as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * csAcceptsControls is added to ControlStyle.
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the toolbar.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvToolBar.HintColor
Summary
  Determines the color of the hint boxes for the Help Hints for the toolbar.
Description
  Use HintColor to specify the hint box color. A default color value of clInfoBk is set for the
  HintColor property in the constructor when the application is created. To change the HintColor
  assign it a new TColor value.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvToolBar.Menu
Summary
  Indicates the menu that the toolbar must reproduce.
Description
  This property is an overlaod of the inherited property from TToolBar. However, it accepts
  a TJvMainMenu and takes advantage of the menu modification notification to automatically
  update itself when the menu is changed.
See Also
  TToolbar, TJvMainMenu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvToolBar.OnMouseEnter
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves over the toolbar.
Description
  \Write an OnMouseEnter event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse over the 
  toolbar.
See Also
  OnMouseLeave
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvToolBar.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the toolbar.
Description
  \Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  toolbar. For example, you can use this event to undo changes that were made in an OnMouseEnter
  event handler.
See Also
  OnMouseEnter
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvToolBar.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color property for the parent of the tool bar changes.
Description
  \Write an OnParentColorChange event to take specific action when the ParentColor property changes.
